  "design_notes": "We designed this medium-difficulty chart to perfectly mirror the energetic flow of the track. The chart begins with comfortable, sparse quarter and half notes to establish the beat in S0, gradually layering in more complex rhythms as the build-up approaches. The transition section S1 features cascading hold releases that deliver a satisfying tactile tension release right as the main drop hits. During the S2 drop, we utilize an intense stream of eighth notes with light crossovers and jumps placed precisely on accents to maximize physical engagement without overwhelming the player. In the S3 outro, we cool down with a rhythmic taper but keep enough grid steps to prevent any long silent pauses.",
